{"id":"kai-001","text":"清晨，他轻轻打开了窗户。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-002","text":"春天到了，桃花陆续开放。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-003","text":"司机把车开到学校门口。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-004","text":"会议将在下午三点召开。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-005","text":"请把客厅的灯打开。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-006","text":"学校开设了一门书法课。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-007","text":"商店每天早上八点开门。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-008","text":"火车缓缓开出了车站。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-009","text":"医生为病人开了一张处方。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-010","text":"公司正在开发新的产品。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-011","text":"这条山路十分开阔平坦。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-012","text":"孩子开心地笑开了花。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-013","text":"他离开家乡已有十年。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-014","text":"运动会的开幕式非常精彩。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-015","text":"轮船离开码头驶向远方。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-016","text":"她开了一家安静的小书店。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-017","text":"请开动脑筋想一想办法。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-018","text":"工人们开采出了新的矿层。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-019","text":"这张支票由银行开具。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-020","text":"他们在河边开辟了一片菜园。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-021","text":"雨后天空开始放晴。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-022","text":"老师开导他要勇敢面对困难。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-023","text":"大门一开，观众依次入场。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-024","text":"这辆公交车开得很平稳。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-025","text":"她开口唱起了家乡的歌。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-026","text":"村民们开荒种下了玉米。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-027","text":"书桌上摊开着一幅地图。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-028","text":"我们分开行动能节省时间。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-029","text":"他开玩笑说自己迷路了。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-030","text":"水烧开以后再放入面条。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-031","text":"游客沿着新开通的步道上山。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-032","text":"花园里的月季开得正艳。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-033","text":"他开诚布公地说明了情况。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-034","text":"新学期将在九月初开学。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-035","text":"展览馆今天正式对外开放。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-036","text":"她开列了一份采购清单。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-037","text":"春风吹开了河面的薄冰。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-038","text":"年轻人应当开阔自己的眼界。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-039","text":"裁缝用剪刀把布料剪开。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-040","text":"天空的乌云渐渐散开了。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-041","text":"他开车时始终遵守交通规则。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-042","text":"全班围绕这个问题展开讨论。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-043","text":"请把收音机开小一点。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-044","text":"新开的餐馆生意很好。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-045","text":"浪花在船头向两边分开。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-046","text":"他揭开锅盖闻到了饭香。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-047","text":"社区为老人开办了食堂。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-048","text":"孩子用钥匙开了院门。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-049","text":"冰雪融化后，江面开始通航。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"kai-050","text":"听到好消息，大家眉开眼笑。","target_char":"开","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
